      '\u003ch2\u003eWhat\'s in it for you\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFlexible working - Our core hours are 10-4\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eRemote working - 1 day a week\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e25 days holiday + Bank Holidays\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eLength of service holiday boosts (2 days extra)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAt least 5% contribution pension scheme\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eTake 5 days each year to attend conferences and we’ll cover the cost including hotel and travel. (Includes international travel)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWe’ll pay for AWS architect certifications or similar\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eIf you need a book, we’ll buy the book\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFurther your career with our progression matrix\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e24hr employee assistance programme / Dedicated Mental Health first aiders\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e£2 gym membership\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eThe people\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHere at AO we hire against our values (Smart, Bold, Fun, Driven and Care).\nOur culture is vital to our success. The AO motto is *Treat every customer like you’d expect your gran to be treated and make decisions your mum would be proud of.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eOur AO’ers don’t just go through the motions it just isn’t our thing. We don’t follow trends, we set them.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eThe role\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eC# .Net AWS React\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eYou’ll be an integral part of an award-winning team, working to find ways that make the customer experience totally effortless. There is a variety of teams we’re hiring for so let’s have a chat about which one suits you best.\nWhen it comes to technology we trust you to make the right decisions whether that be MongoDB or DynamoDB.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWe don’t "Do" Agile, we take the scientific method.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWe’re eager to find out if we’re doing things right. We work hard to find out quickly and without betting the farm whether we’re on the right track.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eWho are AO?\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWe’re in the business of better tomorrows for customers. We may sell everything from washing machines to PlayStations, but putting smiles on our customers’ faces is at the heart of everything we do. #aoletsgo\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eInterested?\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePlease respond using \u003ca href="https://aoworld.redirect.your-jobresponse.com/software_developer_bolton/259443/V819/apply"\u003ethis link!\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eNo recruitment agencies please.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n',
