    url:
      "https://jobs.github.com/positions/e5d4f0b3-5732-4d0c-9cd0-ba07e08fc564",
    created_at: "Thu Nov 14 08:39:50 UTC 2019",
    company: "De VakantieDiscounter",
    company_url: "https://www.vakantiediscounter.nl",
    location: "Amsterdam",
    title: "Senior Scala Engineer",
    description:
      '\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eVakantieDiscounter (Elmar Reizen BV) is the leading online travel agency in The Netherlands where our customers experience an easier and more comfortable way of booking their holiday: \u003ca href="https://www.vakantiediscounter.nl"\u003ewww.vakantiediscounter.nl\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWe are looking for a Senior Software Engineer that will join our growing development department, where you will be part of an agile feature team. Your talent and experience with software development on the JVM will help us become more innovative, improve our productivity, and continue to live up to our high standards. Your focus will be on the Travel Platform that connects Tour Operator inventories to our website by processing large amounts of data for efficient search in our search solution and facilitates booking via our API integration layer.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAll systems are built in-house with our own international development teams leverage technologies such as:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eScala, Akka HTTP and the Play framework for a scalable stateless REST back-end\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eApache Spark, for distributed data processing\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eHELM, Kubernetes for running our systems on GCP\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eClojure/ClojureScript for our website\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eA/B experiments, for sensible decision making\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eYou will be writing lots of high-quality code that goes to production continuously and spend ±10% on R\u0026amp;D to find the next big thing.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eYour skills and qualifications\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eYou are a seasoned Scala Engineer (4+ years) with solid experience working in an Agile environment\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eYou have a deep understanding of the JVM and code optimizations\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eYou have experience with Spark, Hadoop, or other distributed data processing platforms\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eYou have experience with DevOps and improving CI/CD pipelines\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eYou know functional programming and have a passion for learning and sharing your knowledge\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWe consider it a plus if you have experience with:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCats, Scalaz, functional programming libraries\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eKubernetes, Docker, container-based deployments\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eClojure and/or ClojureScript\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eOpen Source; because we contribute back to the ecosystem\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat we offer\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCompetitive remuneration package\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eA developer-focused workspace at our Amsterdam office\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eA fast-growing and flat organization with the possibility of flexible working hours and benefits in terms - of health, pension, and fun initiatives, team buildings, and events\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eThe opportunity to develop through courses, conferences, and events\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e24 paid holidays and 6 ATV days\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDiscount on your holiday trips\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSupport with relocation (visa, housing, 30% tax ruling)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAbout De VakantieDiscounter\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe VakantieDiscounter (Elmar Reizen BV) is an online travel agency from the Benelux and was founded over 20 years ago. From 2009 to 2019, the company has grown its revenue 50x. At the moment, VakantieDiscounter is embarking on an internationalization journey, starting with Germany and further expanding into several other countries in Europe.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe company is continuously focused on innovative improvements and quality, not only with regards to the platform but also in terms of channels to reach and support the customer. The ever-prevailing goal is to make it easier and more comfortable for the customer to select a nice holiday.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe vibrant VakantieDiscounter office, with an international team of 90 people, is located on the Amsterdam canals in the center of the city. The organization is flat, democratic and based on trust, and employees have a lot of freedom in achieving success through their own preferred approach.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eQuestions?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIs this the job for you? Respond quickly to this vacancy! We would like to receive your CV via the application button below. Do you have any questions? Then contact our CTO, Sjors Grijpink at \u003ca href="mailto:sgrijpink@elmar.nl"\u003esgrijpink@elmar.nl\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n',
    how_to_apply:
      '\u003cp\u003eEmail you resume to \u003ca href="mailto:sgrijpink@elmar.nl"\u003esgrijpink@elmar.nl\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n',
